} in group","deselectAllInGroup":"Deselect all {symbol} in group","selectAllTokensInGroup":"Select all tokens in group","deselectAllTokensInGroup":"Deselect all tokens in group"},"PortfolioCollectionTooltipContent":{"error":"Unable to load collection data"},"PortfolioTokenTooltipContent":{"held":"HELD","usdTotal":"USD TOTAL","gain":"GAIN","avgCost":"AVG COST","error":"Unable to load token data"},"Careers":{"learnMore":"Learn More"},"AboutPage":{"heroTitle":"About OpenSea","heroDescription":"OpenSea is building the exchange for the ownership economy — a future where making is owning, taste is earning, prediction pays, and every intelligence, human or artificial, trades value without asking permission.","teamTitle":"Leadership Team & Advisors","missionTitle":"What We Stand For","missionSubtitle":"The principles that guide how we build, ship, and operate.","missionValue1Title":"Today, not tomorrow.","missionValue1Description":"Bias to action, ship early and often, culture of urgency as a self-evident philosophy. Slowness anywhere justifies slowness everywhere.","missionValue2Title":"Be a futurist","missionValue2Description":"Tinkerer and technologist. Get your hands dirty at the fractal edge of technology. Accelerationist, positive view of the future. Authentically engaged in some domain of tech.","missionValue3Title":"Dive deep","missionValue3Description":"Multiple standard deviations above the norm in detail orientation. Fearlessness with complexity. Never leaves a conclusion at the surface level — always goes a click deeper into the “why” and “how.”","milestonesTitle":"Our Journey","milestonesSubtitle":"From a two-person startup to the world\'s leading marketplace for digital assets.","milestone2017Title":"Founded","milestone2017Description":"Devin Finzer and Alex Atallah launch OpenSea as the first open marketplace for NFTs.","milestone2018Title":"Y Combinator","milestone2018Description":"OpenSea joins YC\'s Winter 2018 batch and raises its first seed round.","mile