on":"Tokens with limited liquidity in liquidity pools - could potentially become illiquid"},"INAPPROPRIATE_CONTENT":{"title":"Inappropriate Content","description":"Token metadata contains inappropriate content"},"HIGH_TRANSFER_FEE":{"title":"High Transfer Fee","description":"The token transfer fees are unusually high"},"HIGH_BUY_FEE":{"title":"High Buy Fee","description":"The token buy fee is excessively high"},"HIGH_SELL_FEE":{"title":"High Sell Fee","description":"The token sell fee is excessively high"},"HONEYPOT":{"title":"Honeypot","description":"This token might pose a honeypot risk. It is advised to conduct due diligence before interacting to prevent any potential financial loss"},"SPAM_TEXT":{"title":"Spam Text","description":"The metadata associated with this token contains suspicious, spam-like text that may be deceptive"},"INSUFFICIENT_LOCKED_LIQUIDITY":{"title":"Insufficient Locked Liquidity","description":"The lack of adequately locked or burned liquidity leaves the token vulnerable to sudden liquidity withdrawals, potentially causing market instability"},"CONCENTRATED_SUPPLY_DISTRIBUTION":{"title":"Concentrated Supply Distribution","description":"The majority of the token\'s supply is held by the top token holders, posing a risk of centralized price manipulation"},"UNSELLABLE_TOKEN":{"title":"Unsellable Token","description":"Dynamic analysis indicates that the token is unsellable"},"WASH_TRADING":{"title":"Wash Trading","description":"This token exhibits signs of wash trading, where artificial transactions inflate its trading volume. Such manipulation can mislead investors about the token\'s actual market activity and demand"},"FAKE_VOLUME":{"title":"Fake Volume","description":"A significant portion of the trade volume is artificially generated by a small subset of trade bots, masking the token\'s true trading activity"},"HIDDEN_SUPPLY_BY_KEY_HOLDER":{"title":"Hidden Supply by Key Holder","description":"Most of the token\'s supply is controlled by a major holder leveraging sock puppet accounts, often the token\'s minter or an early buyer who sniped the token at launch"},"FAKE_TRADE_MAKER_COUNT":{"title":"Fake Trade Maker Count","description":"An account fakes the amount of unique trade maker of a token, to create the illusion of high maker count trading the token"},"SANCTIONED_CREATOR":{"title":"Sanctioned Creator","description":"The token\'s creator is sanctioned by a government or financial institution"},"IS_MINTABLE":{"title":"Mintable Token","description":"The token\'s supply can be increased by the contract owner, which may dilute the value of existing holdings"},"TRANSFER_PAUSEABLE":{"title":"Transfer Pauseable","description":"The token\'s transfers can be paused by the contract owner, which may prevent you from selling or transferring your tokens"},"TOKEN_BACKDOOR":{"title":"Token Backdoor","description":"The contract contains hidden functions that could let the deployer drain or manipulate your holdings"},"POST_DUMP":{"title":"Post-Dump","description":"The token\'s price has collapsed following coordinated selling, a pattern commonly seen after a rug pull"},"IMPERSONATOR_MEDIUM_CONFIDENCE":{"title":"Possible Impersonator","description":"The token shows some signs of mimicking the name, branding, or other traits of a well-known and reputable token"},"IMPERSONATOR_HIGH_CONFIDENCE":{"title":"Likely Impersonator","description":"The token strongly matches patterns used to mimic the name, branding, or other traits of a well-known and reputable token"},"IMPERSONATOR_SENSITIVE_ASSET":{"title":"Impersonates Sensitive Asset","description":"The token attempts to impersonate a sensitive asset, such as a stablecoin or other widely trusted token"},"NON_TRANSERABLE":{"title":"Non-Transferable Token","description":"This token cannot be transferred once acquired, which may prevent you from selling or moving it"},"TRANSFER_FROM_REVERTS":{"title":"Transfers Revert","description":"Attempts to transfer this token consistently fail onchain, which may leave you unable to sell or move it"},"FREEZE_INSTRUCTION_TRIGGERED":{"title":"Freeze Triggered","description":"Token accounts have been frozen — you may be unable to transfer or sell this token"},"SUSPICIOUS_FUND_TRAIL":{"title":"Suspicious Fund Trail","description":"Funds associated with this token have moved through a suspicious trail of transactions"},"COMPROMISED_TOKEN":{"title":"Compromised Token","description":"This token\'s contract or associated accounts show signs of being compromised, putting your holdings at risk"},"title":"{count} {count, plural, one {warning} other {warnings}} for {symbol}"},"useSwapButtonText":{"swap":"Swap","wrap":"Wrap","unwrap":"Unwrap","buy":"Buy","sell":"Sell","deposit":"Deposit","withdraw":"Withdraw"},"SwapImpact":{"swapImpact":"Swap Impact","swapImpactTooltip":"This swap may have a high impact on the price of the token"},"SwapConfirmationModal":{"highSwapImpact":"High Swap Impact","cancel":"No, Cancel","highSlippageWarning":"High Slippage","multipleWarnings":"Warning","impactDescription":"This swap may reduce your return by <impact></impact>.","slippageDescription":"Your max slippage is set to <slippage></slippage>, which may result in a significantly worse exchange rate than expected.","continue":"Do you still want to continue?","confirm":"Yes, I\'m Sure"},"MaxSlippageTooltip":{"description":"The maximum percentage your execution price can differ from the quoted price. If the difference exceeds this percentage, the trade will fail to prevent worse-than-expected rates"},"SideSheetFlows":{"title":"Something went wrong!","description":"An unexpected error occurred. Please try again.","reset":"Reset"},"SwapModule":{"swapping":"Swapping...","swapSuccessful":"Swap successful"},"SwapToastContent":{"title":"Swap successful","pendingTitle":"Swapping"},"TransferToastContent":{"title":"Transfer successful"},"BulkTokenTransferFlow":{"formTitle":"Transfer {count, plural, one {# token} other {# tokens}}","recipientL