ique Callers (7d)","uniqueCallers24h":"{count} in 24h","avgLatency":"Avg Latency","p95Latency":"p95: {ms}ms","latencyMs":"{ms}ms","volume7d":"Creator Volume (7d)","volume24h":"{amount} in 24h","lastActive":"Last active: {time}","detailTab":"Detail","activityTab":"Activity","accessRequirements":"Access Requirements","recentActivity":"Recent Activity"},"ToolHealthSummary":{"liveHealthy":"Live & Healthy","stale":"Stale","avgLatency":"Avg: {ms}ms","p95Latency":"p95: {ms}ms","lastHeartbeat":"Last heartbeat: {time}","lastActive":"Last active: {time}","onchainHashVerified":"Onchain hash verified","hashMismatch":"Manifest hash doesn\'t match"},"ToolActivitySection":{"noActivity":"No activity yet. Activity will appear here as the tool is used.","paymentEvent":"Payment","usage":"Tool call","creatorPayment":"Creator payment","creatorPaymentTooltip":"This payment was sent to the creator\'s address, which is shared across multiple tools. We can\'t determine which specific tool was used."},"SchemaTable":{"parameter":"Parameter","type":"Type","description":"Description","fields":"Fields: {fields}"},"PopularCollectiblesSlider":{"heading":"Popular collectibles","description":"The most sought-after cards collectors are chasing right now.","pikachu":"Pikachu","charizard":"Charizard","mew":"Mew","mbappe":"Kylian Mbappé","blueEyesWhiteDragon":"Blue-Eyes White Dragon","darkMagician":"Dark Magician","michaelJordan":"Michael Jordan","wemby":"Victor Wembanyama","ohtani":"Shohei Ohtani","kobeBryant":"Kobe Bryant","cristianoRonaldo":"Cristiano Ronaldo","wayneGretzky":"Wayne Gretzky"},"PhysicalCollectiblesTopSales":{"title":"Top sales this past week","eyebrow":"Top sales","description":"The biggest trades across all trading card collections in the past seven days"},"PhysicalCollectiblesValueProps":{"eyebrow":"Why OpenSea","heading":"Trade physical cards","subheading":"Partner platforms grade, vault, and insure the physical cards. OpenSea brings their collections together so you can trade them instantly from one wallet.","props":{"authenticated":{"title":"Authenticated & graded","description":"Graded and authenticated by the issuing platform, so you know what you\'re getting."},"ownership":{"title":"True ownership","description":"An NFT in your wallet proves ownership; the partner holds the original."},"liquidity":{"title":"One place to trade","description":"Browse multiple partner platforms and trade 24/7 in one marketplace."},"instant":{"title":"Settles in seconds","description":"Trades clear in seconds, with pricing and history you can verify."}}},"PhysicalCollectiblesHowItWorks":{"eyebrow":"Simple by design","heading":"How it works","subheading":"Partner platforms handle the physical card. You trade the digital version. Here\'s how it fits together.","stepLabel":"Step {number}","steps":{"browse":{"title":"Browse & buy","description":"Explore graded cards from partner platforms across Pokémon, sports, and more. Buy straight from your wallet on OpenSea."},"own":{"title":"Own the NFT","description":"The partner platform stores, insures, and authenticates the physical card while a matching NFT lands in your wallet as proof of ownership."},"redeem":{"title":"Trade or redeem","description":"Hold it, trade it anytime, or redeem it directly with the issuing platform to have the physical card sent to you."}}},"PhysicalCollectiblesFaq":{"eyebrow":"Questions","heading":"Frequently asked questions","subheading":"How buying and trading physical collectibles works on OpenSea, and who handles what.","items":{"whatArePhysicalCollectibles":{"question":"What are physical collectibles?","answer":"They\'re real-world items, like graded trading cards, that a partner platform authenticates and stores, then represents as an NFT. Owning the NFT means you own the underlying physical card held by that platform."},"howAuthentication":{"question":"Who authenticates and stores the cards?","answer":"The partner platform that issues each collection handles grading, authentication, insurance, and storage of the physical card. OpenSea is the marketplace where you discover and trade those collections, it doesn\'t store or ship the physical items."},"canIRedeem":{"question":"Can I redeem the physical item?","answer":"Redemption is offered by the issuing platform, not OpenSea. When supported, you redeem the NFT directly with that platform to have the physical card shipped to you, after which the NFT is retired."},"howToBuy":{"question":"How do I buy a physical collectible?","answer":"Connect your wallet, browse the collections surfaced from partner platforms, and complete your purchase just like any other item on OpenSea."},"whatChains":{"question":"Which networks are supported?","answer":"These collections live on the networks supported by each partner platform. The network is shown on every item before you buy."}}},"ToolPackModals":{"createTitle":"Create a pack","createDescription":"Organize your saved tools into themed packs you can share with others.","namePlaceholder":"Pack name","nameRequired":"Pack name is required","createFailed":"Could not create pack. Try again.","creating":"Creating…","create":"Create","renameTitle":"Rename pack","renameFailed":"Could not rename pack. Try again.","saving":"Saving…","save":"Save","deleteTitle":"Delete pack","deleteDescription":"Are you sure you want to delete \\"{name}\\"? Tools in this pack will remain in your saved tools.","deleteFailed":"Could not delete pack. Try again.","deleting":"Deleting…","delete":"Delete","cancel":"Cancel"},"ToolPacksList":{"title":"Packs","createPack":"Create pack","allTools":"All saved tools","packOptions":"Pack options","rename":"Rename","share":"Copy link","linkCopied":"Link copied to clipboard","shareFailed":"Could not copy link","deletePack":"Delete","createFirstPack":"Create your first pack","newPack":"New"},"MoveToPackMenu":{"menuLabel":"Pack actions","newPack":"+ New pack","searchPlaceholder":"Search packs","noMatchingPacks":"No packs match","moveTo":"Move to {name}","